      "rationale": "Linear elastic model appropriate for stiffness and yield-force QoIs in the pre-yield regime. Titanium alloy (Ti-6Al-4V) material properties sourced from ASTM F136. Contact interfaces at screw-rod and rod-block interfaces modeled with frictional contact (mu=0.2) consistent with literature. Model form limitations acknowledged for post-yield behavior but are outside the COU scope."
