      "rationale": "Material properties from certified material test reports for Ti-6Al-4V per ASTM F136. Screw geometry from CMM measurements of production parts (n=3). One-at-a-time sensitivity analysis performed for elastic modulus (+/-5%) and friction coefficient (+/-50%); stiffness QoI sensitivity < 3% for all perturbations."
    },
    {
