      "rationale": "Testing performed at a single ASTM F1717 standard offset distance (50 mm) and single loading rate (5 mm/min). Only one test condition evaluated, achieving Gradation 1. This factor is below the required level; the gap is accepted given that the single condition corresponds directly to the regulatory submission scenario and that model predictions are conservative relative to the mean experimental response."
