    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single below-required factor (Test conditions, achieved 1 vs. required 2) is accepted on the basis that the single test condition directly corresponds to the regulatory submission scenario and that FEA predictions are conservative relative to experimental means across all three QoIs. All quantitative acceptance criteria (E/uval < 1.96, QoI difference < 10%) are satisfied. The overall credibility evidence is judged sufficient to support the intended use at Medium assurance level.",
